    <h2 class="section-heading" id="contribute">Contribute</h2>
    <p>Scholars interested in contributing essays or blog posts to the collection should consult the <%= link_to 'CFP page', :controller => '/pages', :action => 'cfps' %>.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Digital Humanities practitioners interested in contributing ideas or code to the project are encouraged to contact us through the contact form below and/or to be begin working with our code on Github. We welcome your ideas for the project!</p>
    <br>
    <p>We also invite DH practitioners to explore the data made available through our APIs.</p>

    <h2 class="section-heading" id="contact-us">Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Please use the form below to contact the editorial and development teams with your feedback, questions, and ideas:</p>

    <%= form_for @message, :url => about_path(:anchor => 'message-form') do |form| %>

      <% flash.each do |key, value| %>
        <%= content_tag(:div, value, :class => "flash #{key}") %>
      <% end %>

      <div class="row">
        <%= form.label 'name:', :class => "field--label" %><%= form.text_field :name, :class => "field--input" %>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <%= form.label 'email:', :class => "field--label" %><%= form.text_field :email, :class => "field--input"  %>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <%= form.label 'subject:', :class => "field--label" %><%= form.text_field :subject, :class => "field--input" %>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <%= form.label 'body:', :class => "field--label" %><%= form.text_area :body, :class => "field--textarea" %>
      </div>

      <div class="row row-submit">
         <%# recaptcha_tags %>
        <%= form.submit "Send", :class => "field--button" %>
      </div>

    <% end %>
